| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1716 — Recovery Inhibition (medusa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4dc0c995-28e2-5449-9949-6d5433fc4588"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
